\begin{alignat*}{1}
K & =(\frac{\alpha A}{2}-\frac{\alpha-2}{4a})+\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{\alpha^{2}A^{2}+\frac{(\alpha-2)^{2}}{4a^{2}}-\frac{\alpha A(\alpha-4)}{a}}
