\begin_inset Formula $K=A_{t,2}+\pi\xi_{2}$
\end_inset

.
 For the solutions 
\begin_inset Formula $K_{1}^{*}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $K_{2}^{*}$
\end_inset

 the indirect utility is 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\alpha}{2}log(K_{1}^{*2}-aK_{1}^{*})-\frac{3\alpha}{2}log(K_{2}^{*2}-aK_{2}^{*})+(1-\alpha)log(\frac{K_{1}^{*}-A}{\pi})$
\end_inset

.
 The solution indicates that a higher i.e.
